    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Fuel Cost Per Trip Calculator</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Estimate your trip fuel cost using any efficiency unit. Supports MPG, L/100km, and km/L with prices in liters or gallons.</p>

    <div data-controller="fuel-cost-trip-calculator" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="fuel-cost-trip-trip-distance" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1.5">Trip Distance</label>
